Folly Beach Tides

About this website

Just a simple web-app for checking current tide levels in Charleston, SC. The tide data comes from the NOAA. Weather data comes from Open Weather Map. The website is free to use and doesn't track any cookies or collect any data.

You can add the "app" to your phone home screen by selecting "add to home screen" in Safari (iPhone) or Chrome (Android) and it will appear like a normal app on your phone.

Forked from Rob Cavanaugh
